Filezoo is a simple visual disk usage program that shows the sizes of the files
in the current directory (or in the directory passed to it as an argument.) It
uses Cairo for the drawing and Gtk# for the windows.

Requirements:
  mono
  libgtk2.0-cil
  libmono-cairo2.0-cil

Compile by:
  gmcs -pkg:gtk-sharp-2.0 -r:Mono.Cairo filezoo.cs dirstats.cs

Usage:
  filezoo.exe [directory]
